700051f-a.title: Bronx: 135th Street (East) - Canal Street (West)
700051f-a.text:
(1)
East 135th Street, east from Canal Street West. I the background appears part of the area that is being constructed into the
westerly approach to the Triborough Bridge.
July 29, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The sare, as seen from Rider Ave., one block farther east.
July 29, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
